## Rust Crate Dependencies (linked, not vendored)

The following Rust crates are used as dependencies and linked into the
native library. They are resolved by Cargo at build time and are NOT
included in this repository.

  libc 0.2           — MIT OR Apache-2.0
  freetype 0.7       — MIT (optional: sge-freetype feature)
  freetype-sys        — MIT (optional: sge-freetype feature)
  rapier2d 0.22      — Apache-2.0 (optional: sge-physics feature)
  image 0.25         — MIT OR Apache-2.0 (optional: android feature)

## Scala/Java Dependencies (resolved at build time)

All Scala and Java dependencies are resolved via Maven/Ivy repositories
at build time and are NOT included in this repository. Notable dependencies:

  kindlings-jsoniter-json  — Apache-2.0
  jsoniter-scala           — MIT
  sttp-client4             — Apache-2.0
  scala-xml                — Apache-2.0
  scribe                   — MIT
  scalajs-dom              — MIT
  gears                    — Apache-2.0
  munit                    — Apache-2.0 (test only)
  playwright               — Apache-2.0 (test only)

For the complete list, see build.sbt.
